{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"99ce72a659","title":"同周恩来、王洪文的谈话（节录）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c8d64028d5","index":0,"year":1974,"month":12,"day":23,"articleId":"99ce72a659","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"四人帮","id":"264b63d816","type":"主题"},{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"邓小平","id":"5bd9678625","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"王洪文","id":"8e2c446eb1","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"},{"name":"邓小平","id":"fb776baaf9","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3e88562e9e","type":"title","text":"同周恩来、王洪文的谈话（节录）","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"99ce72a659","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2fffd50239","type":"paragraph","text":"（毛摇着手对王洪文说）不要搞四人帮！团结起来！四个人搞在一起不好！","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"99ce72a659","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7aabe69ba8","type":"paragraph","text":"（王洪文涨红着脸，点头说，以后不搞了。）","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"99ce72a659","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"55a688c887","type":"paragraph","text":"明年一月起，外宾我不见了。要求见。我也不见了。我吃饭、睡觉还好，游了五次泳。就是讲话、肺、腿。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"99ce72a659","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"90c11968a0","type":"paragraph","text":"（谈到邓小平时说）他（邓）政治思想强，Political（政治）比他（用手指王洪文）强，他［指王洪文］没有邓小平强。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"99ce72a659","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3140cf7719","type":"paragraph","text":"我看小平做个军委副主席。军委副主席、第一副总理兼总参谋长。人材难。［注：毛当时在纸上写了“人材难”三个字，写到此处，周恩来马上说出来：人材难得，毛就把笔放下了。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"99ce72a659","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"33ad77f2ec","type":"paragraph","text":"江青有野心。你们看有没有？（沉默片刻）我看是有。我比你们了解她，几十年。我对她做了工作。搞乱了，三件事，批林批孔批走后门，又不告诉我。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"99ce72a659","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"51080bdfd9","type":"paragraph","text":"（注：这是毛泽东在长沙的谈话。此件根据中央办公厅秘书局提供的唐闻生、王海容的记录稿。）","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"99ce72a659","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}